---
// Gains Section
// "Menos retrabalho, mais previsibilidade"
---

<section class="py-[6rem] bg-[#0A0515] relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <!-- World Class Background System -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 opacity-[0.05] mix-blend-overlay" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=%220 0 200 200%22 xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cfilter id=%22noiseFilter%22%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=%22fractalNoise%22 baseFrequency=%220.8%22 numOctaves=%223%22 stitchTiles=%22stitch%22/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 filter=%22url(%23noiseFilter)%22/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full z-0">
        <div class="absolute top-[20%] right-[10%] w-[60vw] h-[60vw] bg-[#5B21B6] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[120px] opacity-20 animate-aurora-slow"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-[1.5rem] relative z-30">
    
    <div class="max-w-[50rem] mx-auto text-center">
      
      <h2 class="text-[3rem] md:text-[3.5rem] lg:text-[4rem] font-bold text-white mb-[1.5rem] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight drop-shadow-md">
        Menos retrabalho, <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#A78BFA] to-[#6D28D9] animate-gradient-text">mais previsibilidade</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-[#D4D4D4] mb-[3rem] leading-relaxed">
        Centralize sua operação e elimine o caos. Com a Wikimee, você tem visibilidade total do pipeline, reduz falhas de comunicação e entrega no prazo, sempre.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-[1.5rem] mb-[4rem] w-full">
        <!-- 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-[2rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[1rem] border border-[#8B5CF6]/20 hover:border-[#8B5CF6]/50 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(139,92,246,0.2)] animate-float-1">
          <div class="mb-[1.5rem] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 text-[#A78BFA] group-hover:text-white">
             <svg class="w-[3rem] h-[3rem]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[1.25rem] font-medium text-white text-center">Aprovações 3x mais rápidas</span>
        </div>
        <!-- 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-[2rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[1rem] border border-[#8B5CF6]/20 hover:border-[#8B5CF6]/50 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(139,92,246,0.2)] animate-float-2">
          <div class="mb-[1.5rem] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 text-[#A78BFA] group-hover:text-white">
             <svg class="w-[3rem] h-[3rem]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[1.25rem] font-medium text-white text-center">Histórico automático</span>
        </div>
        <!-- 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-[2rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[1rem] border border-[#8B5CF6]/20 hover:border-[#8B5CF6]/50 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(139,92,246,0.2)] animate-float-3">
          <div class="mb-[1.5rem] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 text-[#A78BFA] group-hover:text-white">
             <svg class="w-[3rem] h-[3rem]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[1.25rem] font-medium text-white text-center">Clientes mais felizes</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <button 
          onclick="openModal()"
          class="px-[2.5rem] py-[1rem] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#7C3AED] to-[#DB2777] hover:brightness-110 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-all duration-200 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(124,58,237,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(124,58,237,0.6)] text-[1.125rem] hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Agendar Demo
        </button>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes aurora-slow {
    0% { transform: translate(-50%, 0) scale(1); opacity: 0.2; }
    50% { transform: translate(-45%, 10%) scale(1.1); opacity: 0.3; }
    100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0) scale(1); opacity: 0.2; }
  }
  .animate-aurora-slow { animation: aurora-slow 20s infinite alternate ease-in-out; }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
  }
  
  .animate-float-1 { animation: float 7s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .animate-float-2 { animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite 0.5s; }
  .animate-float-3 { animation: float 9s ease-in-out infinite 1s; }
</style>
